You know, I'm so sorry that I hurt you.

1263
01:39:55,587 --> 01:39:56,952
I'm sorry.

1264
01:39:59,825 --> 01:40:04,319
In Vegas, I don't know what happened.
That wasn't me.

1265
01:40:05,531 --> 01:40:07,158
Look, you know me.

1266
01:40:07,866 --> 01:40:09,731
You know what I'm like.

1267
01:40:11,537 --> 01:40:13,027
You know me.

1268
01:40:19,478 --> 01:40:21,343
I need you to trust me.

1269
01:40:22,681 --> 01:40:26,048
<i>And the winner of this year's 2.09</i>

