01:49:34,399 --> 01:49:38,529
- My bus has to leave right away.
- I gotta walk my dog.

1359
01:49:38,637 --> 01:49:41,197
- I'm sorry we're making such a mess.
- Go, go, go, go, go.

1360
01:49:41,306 --> 01:49:44,366
Nice to see you. Have a good night, darling.

1361
01:49:49,914 --> 01:49:51,211
This way!

1362
01:50:02,427 --> 01:50:03,519
Go.

1363
01:50:17,876 --> 01:50:19,241
This way!

1364
01:50:25,150 --> 01:50:27,141
Come on, Jill. Come on!

1365
01:50:37,062 --> 01:50:39,656
Go that way. Throw me the chips.
