1366
01:50:39,764 --> 01:50:42,631
Give me the chips, I'll meet you at Fox's.

1367
01:50:48,707 --> 01:50:50,299
Go, go, go, go!

1368
01:51:01,252 --> 01:51:02,913
Come on, come on.

1369
01:51:06,024 --> 01:51:07,582
Move, move, move!

1370
01:51:11,763 --> 01:51:13,025
Come on.

1371
01:51:14,165 --> 01:51:15,757
Go, go, this way.

