01:51:27,746 --> 01:51:29,577
All right, let's go.

1373
01:51:37,655 --> 01:51:40,146
Go, go, go, go! Airport!

1374
01:51:58,710 --> 01:52:00,337
<i>I never saw Micky Rosa after that.</i>

