01:52:17,862 --> 01:52:20,296
I don't work for Micky anymore.

1379
01:52:23,301 --> 01:52:24,734
Come on, kid.

1380
01:52:26,571 --> 01:52:30,337
Your picture's all over the database.
Your Vegas gig is done.

1381
01:52:31,376 --> 01:52:33,310
But I will give you one night.

1382
01:52:33,411 --> 01:52:36,471
And I can guarantee
