1383
01:52:37,382 --> 01:52:41,148
You'll make a killing, and you'll keep it all.

1384
01:52:44,222 --> 01:52:45,416
Listen.

1385
01:52:46,991 --> 01:52:48,458
My name's Cole.

1386
01:52:50,028 --> 01:52:51,552
Cole Williams.

1387
01:52:53,464 --> 01:52:55,864
You just bring me Micky Rosa, kid.

1388
01:52:56,167 --> 01:52:58,192
I'll take care of the rest.

1389
01:53:00,738 --> 01:53:03,673
Son of a bitch.

1390
01:53:46,317 --> 01:53:48,080
Who the hell are you?

