A hundred grand.

1418
01:56:19,570 --> 01:56:21,595
I'll give it to you.
Just let me walk away. I'll walk away.

1419
01:56:21,706 --> 01:56:24,766
I don't want your money, Micky.
I don't need it.

1420
01:56:30,581 --> 01:56:33,379
But I know someone
who might be interested.

1421
01:56:33,751 --> 01:56:37,847
He's good with numbers, too.
